OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774289156
OL,3,CFan charged with tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match at Carabao Cup final
OL,6,FA football fan has been charged over
OL,7,Fallegedly entering the Carabao Cup
OL,8,Ffinal at Wembley without a ticket in
OL,9,Fthe first charge for tailgating at a
OL,10,Fmatch, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,12,FTailgating, which is when fans get
OL,13,Fthrough stadium turnstiles by walking
OL,14,Fclosely behind ticket holders, became
OL,15,Fa criminal offence ahead of the match,
OL,16,Ffive years after thousands of
OL,17,Fticketless fans stormed the same
OL,18,Fstadium.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
