FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774289156
OL,3,CFan charged with tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match at Carabao Cup final
OL,6,FOffenders across England and Wales who
OL,7,Fare convicted of tailgating face a
OL,8,Ffootball banning order of up to five
OL,9,Fyears as well as a fine of up to
OL,10,F#1,000.
OL,12,FBenjamin Bailey, 27, of Oldham,
OL,13,FGreater Manchester, was arrested at
OL,14,FSunday afternoon's final between
OL,15,FManchester City and Arsenal and
OL,16,Fcharged with tailgating. He will
OL,17,Fappear at Willesden Magistrates' Court
OL,18,Fon 1 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774289156
OL,3,CFan charged with tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match at Carabao Cup final
OL,6,FTwo other men were arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of the same offence at
OL,8,FWembley and remain in police custody.
OL,10,FThere was a 78% reduction in overall
OL,11,Foffences at this year's final, the
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,14,FA total of 20 arrests were made on
OL,15,FSunday, 22 March, compared to 91
OL,16,Farrests at the same fixture last year,
OL,17,Fthe force added.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
