OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774289156
OL,3,CFan charged with tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match at Carabao Cup final
OL,6,FThe arrests this year included seven
OL,7,Ffor affray, one for assault of an
OL,8,Femergency service worker, and one for
OL,9,Fracially aggravated assault.
OL,11,FA man was also arrested on suspicion
OL,12,Fof tailgating on Sunday at Tottenham
OL,13,FHotspur Stadium as the north London
OL,14,Fteam faced Nottingham Forest, police
OL,15,Fsaid. He had been bailed pending
OL,16,Ffurther investigation.
OL,18,FThe legislation was introduced
OL,19,Ffollowing serious disorder when
OL,20,FEngland played Italy at the Euro 2020
OL,21,Ffinal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
