FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774289156
OL,3,CFan charged with tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match at Carabao Cup final
OL,6,FLives were put at risk when supporters
OL,7,Fbroke into Wembley Stadium, a
OL,8,Fsubsequent review by Baroness Louise
OL,9,FCasey found.
OL,11,FThe new laws follow her findings that
OL,12,Fsanctions on breaking into stadiums
OL,13,Fwere weak and that tailgating should
OL,14,Fbecome a criminal offence.
OL,16,FThere was previously no specific legal
OL,17,Fpenalties for attending a football
OL,18,Fgame without a ticket.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774289156
OL,3,CFan charged with tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match at Carabao Cup final
OL,6,FThe Unauthorised Entry to Football
OL,7,FMatches Act also makes it illegal to
OL,8,Fknowingly try to enter a match with
OL,9,Fforged tickets, passes and
OL,10,Faccreditation, as well as by
OL,11,Fpretending to be a member of stadium
OL,12,For playing staff.
OL,14,FIt follows an independent review of
OL,15,Fthe Uefa European Championship final
OL,16,Fheld at Wembley in north London on
OL,17,FJuly 11 2021.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774289156
OL,3,CFan charged with tailgating at
OL,4,Cfootball match at Carabao Cup final
OL,6,FBaroness Casey identified more than 20
OL,7,F"near misses" that could have resulted
OL,8,Fin serious injury or death as a result
OL,9,Fof ticketless individuals trying to
OL,10,Fgain entry, and in some cases
OL,11,Fsucceeding, for the England v Italy
OL,12,Fmatch.
OL,14,FAround 100,000 people travelled to
OL,15,FWembley for the final "of which
OL,16,Fapproximately 2,000 gained entry to
OL,17,Fthe stadium without tickets".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
